---
export const prerender = true;

import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy — Mershal" 
  description="Privacy Policy for Mershal. Read about how we collect, store, use, and protect your information when you browse our website."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 transition-colors duration-200 font-sans py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-2xl">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="space-y-4 pb-10 border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-900 mb-12">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-widest text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-mono">Legal Policies</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Last updated: June 24, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Legal content in Serif -->
      <article class="font-serif text-slate-750 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        <p class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-base md:text-lg">
          At Mershal, accessible from <a href="https://mershal.in" class="underline">https://mershal.in</a>, we respect your privacy. This policy outlines the types of data we record, how we use it, and your rights regarding your personal information.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have additional questions or require more information about our privacy disclosures, contact our team at <a href="mailto:admin@mershal.in" class="underline">admin@mershal.in</a>.
        </p>

        <hr class="border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-900 my-8" />

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="font-serif font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xl">1. Consent</h2>
          <p>
            By browsing our website or subscribing to our newsletters, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="font-serif font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xl">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>
            We only collect personal information that you explicitly submit to us:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 font-sans text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-550 dark:text-slate-400">
            <li><strong>Newsletter subscription:</strong> We collect your email address when you sign up for weekly digests. This data is written directly to our secure Firestore collection.</li>
            <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> When sending a message, we collect your name, email address, subject, and the message content.</li>
            <li><strong>Log Files:</strong> Mershal logs requests to analyze browser types, date timestamps, referring exit pages, and IP addresses. These are for diagnostic monitoring and are not personally identifiable.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="font-serif font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xl">3. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
          <p>
            Mershal utilizes standard cookies to customize page templates and store preferences. Third-party advertising partners (like Google AdSense) may deploy cookies and web beacons on our site. Google uses the DART cookie to serve personalized ads based on visitor logs. Visitors may decline DART cookies by visiting the Google ad network policies.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="font-serif font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xl">4. Third-Party Integrations</h2>
          <p>
            Our policy does not apply to other advertisers or external sites. We advise you to consult the respective privacy policies of these third-party services (such as Google AdSense) for instructions on opting out of tracking.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="font-serif font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-xl">5. GDPR & CCPA User Rights</h2>
          <p>
            Under privacy regulations, users have the right to request copy of their logged data, request absolute deletion of their subscriber records, or object to processing. To exercise these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:admin@mershal.in" class="underline">admin@mershal.in</a> and we will purge all matching records from Firestore within 24 hours.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
